Starting The IR-Runner
======================

   There are different possibilities to start a project:

  1. Shell/Cli
          1> IRRunner <project.irm> LEFT=20 TOP=20 PUBSCREEN=TERM

  2. Workbench
        @{b}*@{ub} Click on IRRunner (once) + shift-doubleclick on the project's
          icon

        @{b}*@{ub} Make sure that the IR_Runner is in the workench searchpath
          (the path set up before @{b}loadwb@{ub} is called in the
          @{b}startup-sequence@{ub}, e.g. @{b}C:@{ub}, @{b}sys:utiltiies@{ub})

          Doubleclick the project's icon. (default tool must be
          correctly set)

        @{b}*@{ub} If you doubleclick the ir-runner a filerequester will
          appear...


@EndNode

@Node "IR-Runner Menus" "ir-master26e.guide/IR-Runner Menus"
@Next "ARexx Port"
@Prev "Starting The IR-Runner"
